# Changelog

## v1.0 — Cao Urban Trainer ASI

**Author:** CaoK1d13

Initial public release of the native ASI source project.

Included systems:

- GUI menu on F5.
- Player Menu and Advanced Player Menu.
- Skin / Model Changer.
- Outfit / Clothes Editor.
- Weapons Menu and Advanced Weapon Menu.
- Vehicle Spawner, Vehicle Tuning, and Vehicle Builder.
- Add-on vehicle list support.
- Garage System.
- NPC Menu and NPC Model Browser.
- Chauffeur / Driver Mode.
- Bodyguards System.
- Enemy Spawner / Battle Arena.
- Scenario Menu.
- Mission / Scenario Creator.
- Free camera support while creating missions.
- Automatic cleanup of nearby ambient NPCs and vehicles while editing missions.
- Object Spawner.
- Animation Menu.
- Screenshot / Cinematic Tools.
- World Control Menu.
- Advanced Teleport Menu.
- Police / Wanted Menu.
- Save / Load Trainer Presets.
- Settings Menu.
- Multi-language support: English, Russian, Chinese, French, German, Japanese, Spanish, Italian.
- Stability improvements for mission entities, menu indexes, bodyguards, weapon toggles, vehicle god mode, and INI parsing.
